name: Cosmo Baby
description: COSMO BABY was born to resurrect the crypto world, and trigger a bull run the likes of which mankind has never seen. It isn’t just another token; it’s a chubby-cheeked champion, a cosmic crusader crawling towards the moon to deliver giggles and gains. COSMO BABY is here to trigger a bull run that will make history books look like comic strips. The fate of the crypto universe lies in the hands of COSMO BABY.
